title: Ultimate Dr. Horrible Torrent
description:
This is it, folks, the Ultimate Dr. Horrible Torrent!

Includes-

* The highest quality available version of the film, NOT transferred from the FLV files, in AVI format

* The highest quality available version of the songs, NOT transferred from the FLV files, in WAV format

* Sheet Music and chords for several songs

* The Captain Hammer comic by Zack Whedon

* Wallpapers

* Cast and Crew Interviews

* Official Artwork and various fan art


***REMEMBER!!!*** Please buy the Official Soundtrack and the DVD when they are released as they will be of much higher quality and packed with extras! Support the wonderful people who made all this possible so we can get more Dr. Horrible content in the future!
